author: Ianthe Jeanne Dugan
title: Former Officials Raise Questions About New LA Times Owner’s Business
text:
When medical entrepreneur Patrick Soon-Shiong bought the embattled Los Angeles Times from owner Tronc Inc. this week, some journalists cheered.
Investors in Dr. Soon-Shiong’s health company have done anything but.
